### x-animation

**1. usage**

	syntax：<%=include%>x-animation(<%=variable%>animation);

	params：

		* <%=variable%>animation --- the composition of the value：

			* animation-name  

			* animation-duration

			* animation-timing-function

			* animation-delay

			* animation-iteration-count

			* animation-direction

			The default value is：none 0 ease 0 1 normal

**2. example**

	div {
		<%=include%>x-animation(test 3s ease);
	}